  "texts": [
    "The comprehensive use of these criteria can provide a more comprehensive assessment of the performance of object detection algorithms.",
    "ConclusionIn summary, this paper discusses the significance and optimization methods of deep learning in the field of traffic scene object detection.",
    "Traffic scene object detection is a key task in fields such as intelligent transport systems and autonomous driving, involving the accurate detection of various objects such as vehicles, pedestrians, and traffic signs.",
    "Deep learning techniques have made significant progress in this field, improving detection accuracy and efficiency.To overcome the challenges in traffic scene object detection, researchers have proposed various optimization methods.",
    "These methods include feature enhancement to extract more informative features for improved detection performance, improvements based on contextual information to better understand the relationships between objects and their surroundings, super-resolution techniques to enhance the detection of small objects, and optimization of loss functions for better training of deep learning models.In conclusion, research in deep learning for traffic scene object detection plays a crucial role in advancing safer and more intelligent traffic systems and autonomous driving technologies."
